data.description: Welcome to Deltona Lakes! This 3-year-old home awaits you. NO HOA! The layout of this home is designed with simplicity and functionality in mind. The open concept kitchen is a highlight, overlooking the great room and featuring a spacious island with plenty of seating. The split floor plan ensures privacy, with the primary bedroom separated on one side of the home. Adams Homes has included many desirable features in this home. The double-pane windows tilt in for easy cleaning, making maintenance a breeze. Stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, 36' cabinets with crown molding provide ample storage space, triple hinged interior 5 panel doors, brushed nickel fixtures and much more. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity. Schedule a showing today and make this house your home!
